data.description: Beautifully updated in 2021, this 3 br 2 ba Single family pool home with AMAZING outdoor living! Not only does this completely furnished home offer almost 1,900sf of living space in a wonderful living room & family room layout, it also offers a massive newly screened pool cage that features an electric heated pool w/ a custom waterfall & remote control LED light system, surround sound (also in the living room) and pocket slider doors off of the master, living room, and one of the guest rooms. The open concept kitchen has a long breakfast bar, large pantry, entry way to rear pool lanai, lots of countertop space, and all of the appliances. Surrounded by tropical landscaping, this home sits on an oversized corner lot and features a wide drive leading to a 2-car garage, room on side of home for boat storage, storage shed, & it has a screened front entry allowing you to completely open up the home on cool Florida days. WIFI access controls the new garage door and the front door keypad lock. Absolutely no damage from hurricane Ian. Great Cape Coral location w/access to the North Bridge and the Midpoint Bridge, plus it is close to LOTS of shopping & dining options. Truly a must see home!
